      <container name="Recalling" eId="container_2">
        <p xml:space="preserve">	<span class="italic">Recalling </span>its previous resolutions on the Joint Inspection Unit, in particular resolutions <a href="https://docs.un.org/en/A/RES/31/192">31/192</a> of 22 December 1976, <a href="https://docs.un.org/en/A/RES/50/233">50/233</a> of 7 June 1996, <a href="https://docs.un.org/en/A/RES/54/16">54/16</a> of 29 October 1999, <a href="https://docs.un.org/en/A/RES/56/245">56/245</a> of 24 December 2001, <a href="https://docs.un.org/en/A/RES/57/284a-b">57/284</a> A and B of 20 December 2002, <a href="https://docs.un.org/en/A/RES/58/286">58/286</a> of 8 April 2004, <a href="https://docs.un.org/en/A/RES/59/267">59/267</a> of 23 December 2004, <a href="https://docs.un.org/en/A/RES/60/258">60/258</a> of 8 May 2006, <a href="https://docs.un.org/en/A/RES/61/238">61/238</a> of 22 December 2006, <a href="https://docs.un.org/en/A/RES/61/260">61/260</a> of 4 April 2007, <a href="https://docs.un.org/en/A/RES/62/226">62/226</a> of 22 December 2007, <a href="https://docs.un.org/en/A/RES/62/246">62/246</a> of 3 April 2008, <a href="https://docs.un.org/en/A/RES/63/272">63/272</a> of 7 April 2009, <a href="https://docs.un.org/en/A/RES/64/262">64/262</a> of 29 March 2010, <a href="https://docs.un.org/en/A/RES/65/270">65/270</a> of 4 April 2011, <a href="https://docs.un.org/en/A/RES/66/259">66/259</a> of 9 April 2012, <a href="https://docs.un.org/en/A/RES/67/256">67/256</a> of 12 April 2013, <a href="https://docs.un.org/en/A/RES/68/266">68/266</a> of 9 April 2014, <a href="https://docs.un.org/en/A/RES/69/275">69/275</a> of 2 April 2015, <a href="https://docs.un.org/en/A/RES/70/257">70/257</a> of 1 April 2016, <a href="https://docs.un.org/en/A/RES/71/281">71/281</a> of 6 April 2017, <a href="https://docs.un.org/en/A/RES/72/269">72/269</a> of 4 April 2018, <a href="https://docs.un.org/en/A/RES/73/287">73/287</a> of 15 April 2018, <a href="https://docs.un.org/en/A/RES/75/270">75/270</a> of 16 April 2021, <a href="https://docs.un.org/en/A/RES/76/261">76/261</a> of 13 April 2022, <a href="https://docs.un.org/en/A/RES/77/279">77/279</a> of 18 April 2023, <a href="https://docs.un.org/en/A/RES/78/276">78/276</a> of 24 April 2024 and <a href="https://docs.un.org/en/A/RES/79/281">79/281</a> of 11 April 2025, </p>
      </container>
      <container name="Reaffirming" eId="container_3">
        <p xml:space="preserve">	<span class="italic">Reaffirming</span> the statute of the Unit<authorialNote marker="1" placement="bottom" eId="authorialNote_1"><p xml:space="preserve">		Resolution <a href="http://undocs.org/A/RES/31/192">31/192</a>, annex.</p></authorialNote> and the unique role of the Unit as the only external and independent system-wide inspection, evaluation and investigation body, </p>
      </container>
      <container name="Having considered" eId="container_4">
        <p xml:space="preserve">	<span class="italic">Having considered</span> the report of the Unit for 2025 and programme of work for 2026<authorialNote marker="2" placement="bottom" eId="authorialNote_2"><p xml:space="preserve">		<span class="italic">Official Records of the General Assembly, Eightieth Session, Supplement No. 34</span> (<a href="https://docs.un.org/en/A/80/34">A/80/34</a>).</p></authorialNote> and the note by the Secretary-General on the report of the Unit for 2025,<authorialNote marker="3" placement="bottom" eId="authorialNote_3"><p xml:space="preserve">		<a href="https://docs.un.org/en/A/80/608">A/80/608</a>.</p></authorialNote></p>
      </container>
